window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Stepsiblings Britney and Trevor have never really gotten along all that well, but when their parents die unexpectedly in a car crash, they decide to join forces to make sure they can maintain their luxurious lifestyle. Together, they develop a foolproof plan to make money, but it involves a great deal of underhanded behavior, a few hidden cameras, secret sexual fantasies, and possible jail time. </p> <p><i>Stepbrother Bad Boy: Tempting Fate</i> is a tantalizing tale told from Britney's perspective as she recounts her subversive relationship and dealings with her stepbrother, including the unavoidable ways they are drawn together by their outlaw, taboo behavior. Filled with shocking twists and turns and achingly erotic moments, it's sure to entertain all of your senses and leave you wanting more from this unlikely duo. </p>"; 
